ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:34:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"746dfd02c208047140093312f318871936373c30","tid":1635201,"uid":160842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:34:17.000Z","msg":"勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n罷工係對個政權最撚有衝擊既抗爭手法，但三罷做左咁撚多次，都係得8.5成功，因為計劃左好撚耐，對香港人黎講，個個都只想被罷工，到呢個地步，你仲想做休息撚，而唔乘勝追擊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但咁撚樣都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<br />\n<br />\n唔撚係話和理非冇用，但勇和齊上齊落唔撚得？"},{"pid":"2ffd208e3aab4dd81d7e17c82c642f3b0797b912","tid":1635201,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:34:27.000Z","msg":"【facebook戰線】大家一齊report曬D垃圾page，等佢地重蹈點新聞嘅覆轍<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eewfbS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eewfbS</a><br />\n<br />\n【地方的手足需要進化】麻煩大家入黎溫下書，睇下烏克蘭係E個時候做左D咩<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejgzzS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejgzzS</a>"},{"pid":"d5ead941001e2acc92e1ce60f606701ef67929d7","tid":1635201,"uid":107671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:34:58.000Z","msg":"咁撚清楚，應該好快搵到仔啦<br />\n推"},{"pid":"02cdc7b7be5fe0fe92cc26ccd3c3a9752fe734c9","tid":1635201,"uid":117265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:35:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"751ea1feff7d8695d303a3f2c3435b23a0ec79ef","tid":1635201,"uid":111898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:35:12.000Z","msg":"兩個同班狗有講有笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8343276b93f2526f1b4e87d9b65fd4be00f993a6","tid":1635201,"uid":326746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:35:23.000Z